T("objc-runtime-error","Objective-C Runtime Error","Runtime errors in dynamic dispatch.","Method not found; wrong class; swizzling","```objc\nMethod method = class_getInstanceMethod(self.class, @selector(myMethod));\nif (method) {\n    IMP imp = method_getImplementation(method);\n    imp(self, @selector(myMethod));\n}\n```","```objc\n// Method swizzling\nMethod original = class_getInstanceMethod(self.class, @selector(viewDidLoad));\nMethod swizzled = class_getInstanceMethod(self.class, @selector(my_viewDidLoad));\nmethod_exchangeImplementations(original, swizzled);\n```"),
T("objc-method-swizzling","Objective-C Method Swizzling","Method swizzling errors.","Wrong method replacement; side effects","```objc\n// Safe swizzling\n- (void)load {\n    static dispatch_once_t onceToken;\n    dispatch_once(&onceToken, ^{\n        Class class = [self class];\n        Method original = class_getInstanceMethod(class, @selector(viewDidLoad));\n        Method swizzled = class_getInstanceMethod(class, @selector(my_viewDidLoad));\n        method_exchangeImplementations(original, swizzled);\n    });\n}\n```","```objc\n- (void)my_viewDidLoad {\n    [self my_viewDidLoad];  // calls original\n    NSLog(@\"viewDidLoad called\");\n}\n```"),
T("objc-nsobject-error","Objective-C NSObject Error","NSObject method errors.","init not called; wrong equality","```objc\n- (instancetype)init {\n    self = [super init];\n    if (self) {\n        // initialize\n    }\n    return self;\n}\n```","```objc\n- (BOOL)isEqual:(id)object {\n    if (self == object) return YES;\n    if (![object isKindOfClass:[self class]]) return NO;\n    return [self.name isEqualToString:((MyClass *)object).name];\n}\n```"),
